type="local"
href="jms-00ME.xml"
addr="jms-00ME"
title="Enumerable set">enumeration</fr:link> <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[e_I\colon  \mathbb {N}\twoheadrightarrow  I]]></fr:tex>; as each <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[A_i]]></fr:tex> is <fr:link
type="local"
href="jms-00ME.xml"
addr="jms-00ME"
title="Enumerable set">enumerable</fr:link>, we may use the <fr:link
type="local"
